<h2>Theme switcher component</h2>
<p>
  The BM Darklight module provides a reusable light/dark/system theme switcher.
  It toggles the <code>data-theme</code> attribute on <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>,
  which can be consumed by CSS (e.g., <code>:root[data-theme="dark"]</code>).
</p>
<h3>Usage</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Attach library: <code>bm_darklight/theme_switcher</code></li>
  <li>Render the component: <code>#theme =&gt; 'bm_darklight_switcher'</code></li>
  <li>Buttons set <code>data-theme</code> to <code>light</code>, <code>dark</code>, or remove it for system.</li>
</ol>
<h3>Demo</h3>
<p>Visit <code>/admin/config/user-interface/bm-darklight/theme-switcher-demo</code> to see the component in action.</p>
